data.title: Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI) Record / Information / Dissemination Section (RIDS) Dead List, 2009
data.meta_description: FBI Rids Deadlist 2009 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document is a list from the FBI of notable or famous individuals who are deceased, for whom the FBI may have files. It includes names, dates of death or other identifying information. Requesters can submit Freedom of Information Act requests for files on individuals from this list by writing to the FBI's Record Information Dissemination Section and including proof of death. The list contains names from organized crime groups like the LCN (La Cosa Nostra) as well as public figures.
